title: Nine Inch Nails Tension 2013 Rehearsals
description:
Here's the much discussed rehearsal tracks made public by www.reflectinginthechrome.com in its original state, with banter and false track starts all cut into separate tracks.

If you're just wanting the audio please visit RITC and download their version - it's tracked specifically to flow better with no extra talking or banter.



Also i'm not affiliated with reflecting in the chrome in any way, shape or form...I just really like those dudes and support the hell out of what they do.

Thanks!
